--[[
    Da7muLibrary  –  Fixed Edition
    Original design by Da7mu

    Changes from original:
      • Dropdown OptionsList now parents to ScreenGui and positions absolutely,
        so it never gets clipped by ScrollingFrames or ClipsDescendants frames.
      • Removed ClipsDescendants = true from ContentContainer.
      • All UserInputService / RunService connections are stored and cleaned up
        on Window:Destroy() — no more global connection leaks.
      • Blur system wrapped in pcall so NearPlaneZ NaN-crashes are silently
        swallowed; the rest of the UI still works if blur fails.
      • Dropdown Outer frame no longer fights AutomaticSize with a fixed Y.
      • Section:Separator() returns self for consistency.
      • Dragging clamped to viewport so the window can't be dragged off-screen.
]]

